OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with patchy rain moving east,
OL,7,Fmainly affecting Moray and western
OL,8,FAberdeenshire. Then the rest of the
OL,9,Fnight will be dry with clear periods.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FSome brightness in the north
OL,12,Fand east at first. Otherwise a mainly
OL,13,Fcloudy and largely dry day. Rain
OL,14,Fspreading east in the evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FWednesday bright with sunny spells and
OL,18,Fa few showers. Cloudy with rain on
OL,19,FThursday, some heavy later. Then
OL,20,Fbrighter again on Friday with sunny
OL,21,Fintervals and a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
